com.intland.codebeamer.persistence.dto

Class LabelDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intland.codebeamer.persistence.dto.base.IdentifiableDto
      • com.intland.codebeamer.persistence.dto.base.NamedDto
        • com.intland.codebeamer.persistence.dto.LabelDto
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaseDto, ReferableDto, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable

    public class LabelDto
extends NamedDto
implements ReferableDto
    A tag/label, that can be associated with entities

    Labels have a special derived property "display name":

    • their "real name" is the actual persistent property
    • their "real name" will be prefixed by PRIVATE_LABEL_PREFIX when their access is private, and this "display name" will be used in the user interface
